OL,6,FA man from Somerset has been sentenced
OL,7,Fto nine years in prison after sexually
OL,8,Fabusing a child and distributing
OL,9,Fthousands of indecent images.
OL,11,FAyden Reader, from Taunton, pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to 19 charges including taking,
OL,13,Fmaking, possessing, and distributing
OL,14,Fthousands of indecent images.
OL,16,FHe also admitted having sexual
OL,17,Factivity with a child.
