OL,6,FIn a hearing at Taunton Crown Court on
OL,7,FFriday 2 February, the court heard how
OL,8,FReader engaged with a teenage girl on
OL,9,Fsocial media in 2021 and began
OL,10,Fmessaging her.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the victim said: "What
OL,13,FAyden has done to me and the way he
OL,14,Fhas treated me has made me less
OL,15,Fbelieving of people.
OL,17,FIf you've been affected by any issues
OL,18,Fraised in this story, advice and
OL,19,Fsupport can be found .
