OL,6,F"When I am anxious, I feel sick, I
OL,7,Fstruggle to sleep and can't cope in
OL,8,Fpublic places without feeling
OL,9,Foverwhelmed.
OL,11,F"It made me re-live what happened and
OL,12,Fmade me feel guilty and shame.
OL,14,F"I am worried that if he would be
OL,15,Freleased from prison, that he might
OL,16,Fmessage me again and, if this happens,
OL,17,Fit will be like a circle for me and
OL,18,Fnever-ending."
