OL,6,FWhile being investigated by police,
OL,7,FReader began messaging young girls on
OL,8,Fsocial media, breaching the terms of
OL,9,Fhis Sexual Harm Prevention Order.
OL,11,FHe also accessed devices he had not
OL,12,Fdeclared or made available to police.
OL,14,FOfficers from Kent Police seized
OL,15,Fvarious devices, where they found 830
OL,16,Fcategory A images - the most serious.
OL,18,FThere were also 973 category B and 610
OL,19,Fcategory C images.
