OL,8,Fsexual activity with a child, and one
OL,9,Fcount of causing a child to engage in
OL,10,Fsexual activity.
OL,12,FHe was also charged with one count of
OL,13,Ftaking indecent images and six counts
OL,14,Fof making indecent images.
OL,16,FHe was charged by Kent Police with:
