OL,6,FThe judge also granted an indefinite
OL,7,FSexual Harm Prevention Order for
OL,8,FReader and an indefinite restraining
OL,9,Forder banning him from contacting the
OL,10,Fvictim for life.
OL,12,FThe officer in the Avon and Somerset
OL,13,Fcase, DC Melanie Downton, said: "I
OL,14,Fwould like to first commend the
OL,15,Fincredibly bravery shown by the victim
OL,16,Fin this case.
OL,18,F"She has shown incredible resilience
OL,19,Fand courage in come forward and
OL,20,Fsupporting our investigation.
