OL,6,F"We have worked in partnership with
OL,7,FKent Police to bring this dangerous
OL,8,Foffender to justice.
OL,10,F"I hope this sentence will give other
OL,11,Fsexual offence victims the courage to
OL,12,Fcome forward and report what has
OL,13,Fhappened to them.
OL,15,F"We have a dedicated child protection
OL,16,Fteam who have a wealth of experience
OL,17,Fand knowledge in investigating
OL,18,Foffences of this nature.
